A taxi passenger was murdered on Wednesday following an alleged taxi war in Eikenhof. The taxi was carrying passengers from Sandton to Palm Springs when it was shot at. According to Captain Kay Makhubele &#8220;three passengers were wounded by gun shots, and one injured by glasses&#8221;. &#8220;The motive of the shooting is unknown at this stage and police are investigating cases of murder and attempted murder&#8221;, said Makhubele. No arrests have been made by the police as yet and police have urged the community to assist should they have information that might help the police.-Aviwe Maxheke